dct_title_s: Comitatus Herefordiensis: Hereford shire.; Comitatvs Herefordiensis: Hereford shire;Province of Herefordshire
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Decorative title cartouche with grapes in the top right corner, and a blank cartouche with open-mouthed faces in the lower right corner. This state was published in atlases by Jan Jansson in 1647 and 1658. From the Jansson Appendix Atlas 1636-1680, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan. 1 map; 37 x 48 cm.
dct_rights_sm: This map is in the public domain.
